    System.out.println(solution.isPowerOfThree2(0));
}
```

This solution checks all integers from 0 to `n` and returns true if any of them are powers of 3. The `allMatch` method is a terminal operation and returns true as soon as it finds a match. The time complexity of this solution is O(n) because it has a single operation per iteration of the stream.

